人吹奏嘅所謂文明國度日本，奴性比香港更嚴重"},{"pid":"1dbc3864d6bb5a18143635e62f0ba3b8e15d19d2","tid":359571,"uid":50574,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-14T19:30:31.000Z","msg":"治安黎講一定差撚過"},{"pid":"2100af2fedb07172508b2bb31f92431329fcd59c","tid":359571,"uid":31323,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-14T19:31:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>波蘭都咁上下<br />\n好撚多波蝗喺英國呃緊福利</blockquote><br />\n點解<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n波蘭經濟好撚差"},{"pid":"2bf6a70ef6ded8e01cd06e9d4e5e66cc6869671e","tid":359571,"uid":41245,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-14T19:32:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>法國 白人定黑人都喺街fing唔做野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咁法國崩潰未<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n人地核能 飛機 軍事 等等係最top個批</blockquote><br />\n同黑手黨有衝突咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n真係歐洲支那<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 支那在一樣有人會為佢地轉移視線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n同講支那點樣有假鈔、偷呃拐騙，之後衝出嚟話支那GDP升咗好多、啲公司賺好多錢一樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n根本問題就係一啲關係都冇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n可以有好top嘅嘢，同樣治安差。唔係點解啲歐洲人成日笑其他歐洲國家話佢地各國一係嘢食差、一係工業差、一係管理差，永遠冇一個國家係冇缺點"},{"pid":"b54c23998c09f1e36cb29dcd9c04de3c7fa0aab7","tid":359571,"uid":48157,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-14T19:55:28.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"077f1813cf7b1ddf03415ca0a4297db6c833dc5b","tid":359571,"uid":60545,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-14T20:00:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>法國 白人定黑人都喺街fing唔做野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咁法國崩潰未<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n人地核能 飛機 軍事 等等係最top個批</blockquote><br />\n同黑手黨有衝突咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n真係歐洲支那<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 支那在一樣有人會為佢地轉移視線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n同講支那點樣有假鈔、偷呃拐騙，之後衝出嚟話支那GDP升咗好多、啲公司賺好多錢一樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n根本問題就係一啲關係都冇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n可以有好top嘅嘢，同樣治安差。唔係點解啲歐洲人成日笑其他歐洲國家話佢地各國一係嘢食差、一係工業差、一係管理差，永遠冇一個國家係冇缺點</blockquote><br />\n支那做到法國一半已經好喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/29.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n法國治安差，但其他嘢都比英國好<br />\n其實你地點去定義一個國家好壞㗎"},{"pid":"9592dc1b2047ad2e1b8e059b7074e01852fe79cf","tid":359571,"uid":106360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-14T20:00:43.000Z","msg":"意粉除左治安差<br />\n啲人真係無乜禮貌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e041559b9f02d924e8fdeb31d737519a7b5ee98f","tid":359571,"uid":130105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-14T20:32:29.000Z","msg":"希臘<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"be708bbaf735e7c0eedf7bd3aa876dd80f0083df","tid":359571,"uid":66246,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-15T00:25:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4142be36f66a423135198b2ade7bcf41820db71b","tid":359571,"uid":62691,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-15T00:34:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實歐洲來講真係得德國、瑞士、英國叫做好少少<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n其他真係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n北歐呢？"},{"pid":"92f3ddf27e7ae39b9713d41c8bc4deec4d89d8fd","tid":359571,"uid":132302,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-