ad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咁法國崩潰未<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n人地核能 飛機 軍事 等等係最top個批</blockquote><br />\n問題咪就係似支那咁<br />\n仲有啲人唔撚做 喺度賣買啲手繩 偷野<br />\n去過法國就明我想講咩<br />\n<br />\n最好一定係英德<br />\n個人去左呢三個國家<br />\n法國真心亂亂地"},{"pid":"c2d3a2db7841df707ffc1b2f019195c59550f758","tid":359571,"uid":51717,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-15T04:18:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>意大利跟本就係歐洲版支那</blockquote><br />\nD扒手同大陸有得揮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n其實大陸最多都係偷。至小唔會大街大巷㩒住你嚟搶。<br />\n意大利。㩒住你嚟搶真係聽得多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你假膠定我認真？<br />\n強國無撳住搶？<br />\n以前公司東莞班強國同事，三十幾人，八成都試過係街俾人夾硬搶嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，我都試過俾人從後電單車搶咗我袋垃圾(準備掉)<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n邊個平行宇宙強國咁太平？"},{"pid":"1d92fe2439479a44a304f4d597fc55c9ee9a3680","tid":359571,"uid":58918,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-15T04:19:19.000Z","msg":"香港有咩好野衰野全部都因為奴性<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"064e4492c105bff5de2a2f4caedc8bbebd6da281","tid":359571,"uid":115516,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-15T04:21:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>意粉除左治安差<br />\n啲人真係無乜禮貌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n係, 仲要勁打尖, 我好記得等巴士佢地打曬尖, manner 係完全同支那冇分別"},{"pid":"642ad9d46ff31aa669fe37d95b58da52eebba869","tid":359571,"uid":66246,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-15T04:26:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>意大利跟本就係歐洲版支那</blockquote><br />\nD扒手同大陸有得揮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n其實大陸最多都係偷。至小唔會大街大巷㩒住你嚟搶。<br />\n意大利。㩒住你嚟搶真係聽得多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你假膠定我認真？<br />\n強國無撳住搶？<br />\n以前公司東莞班強國同事，三十幾人，八成都試過係街俾人夾硬搶嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，我都試過俾人從後電單車搶咗我袋垃圾(準備掉)<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n邊個平行宇宙強國咁太平？</blockquote><br />\n可能佢去開一線城市"},{"pid":"e9c994dd6fe2564257c80187ce31e83ee7c781f9","tid":359571,"uid":130105,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-15T04:27:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>睇黎你未去過東歐一眾窮國<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n去過波蘭，匈牙利，窮係窮，但感覺都安全過意大利，法國</blockquote><br />\n個班窮國係因以前比蘇聯控制行共產<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"71898fbe8533cda04a2ce08713cfeb4c3d63a674","tid":359571,"uid":39846,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-15T05:34:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>睇黎你未去過東歐一眾窮國<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />願詳其聞<br />\n<br />\n未去過</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n百痴ex要追星，貪平，同佢去愛沙尼亞睇演唱會，係成個歐洲tour 最平，幾十歐羅坐前排。<br />\n一落機發現自已luggage 有比人開過嘅feel, 即場check 有冇中招，但又投訴無門。<br />\n都算，坐機場的士都係黑的黎&hellip;&hellip;&hellip; 塔林好細，居然坐左五十歐羅&hellip;&hellip; 問個pk 司機又扮唔識英文&hellip;&hellip;&hellip; <br />\n我又再算，心諗頂多唔free and easy 係酒店一帶行下應該好安全。<br />\n到第日因為我問過酒店姐姐，佢話演唱會場地比較遠，坐的士比較好，ok 見妳又大波又低胸，成隻歐洲吸血鬼咁。咪問佢有冇酒店車？佢話得s class benz, 八十一程，仲話同坐的士差無幾，我心諗，嘩乜咁七貴。<br />\n好啦，睇撚完，本來想叫翻酒店車，但諗下，都八條，坐的士算，屌點知居然坐到良心的士，全程十二蚊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n果一下我勁撚無奈&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip; <br />\n我想像唔到，如果我free and easy 岀下夜街，行下街市冷巷會有幾大煲&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;"},{"pid":"812f04a8172be36da173f6afe57a0187c669859d","tid":359571,"uid":39846,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-15T05:46:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>睇黎你未去過東歐一眾窮國<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />願詳其聞<br />\n<br />\n未去過</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n百痴ex要追星，貪平，同佢去愛沙尼亞睇演唱會，係成個歐洲tour 最平，幾十歐羅坐前排。<br />\n一落機發現自已luggage 有比人開過嘅feel, 即場check 有冇中招，但又投訴無門。<br />\n都算，坐機場的士都係黑的黎&hellip;&hellip;&hellip; 塔林好細，居然坐左五十歐羅&hellip;&hellip; 問個pk 司機又扮唔識英文&hellip;&hellip;&hellip; <br />\n我又再算，心諗頂多唔free and easy 係酒店一帶行下應該好安全。<br />\n到第日因為我問過酒店姐姐，佢話演唱會場地比較遠，坐的士比較好，ok 見妳又大波又低胸，成隻歐洲吸血鬼咁。咪問佢有冇酒店車？佢話得s class benz, 八十一程，仲話同坐的士差無幾，我心諗，嘩乜咁七貴。<br />\n好啦，睇撚完，本來想叫翻酒店車，但諗下，都八條，坐的士算，屌點知居然坐到良心的士，全程十二蚊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n果一下我勁撚無奈&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip; <br />\n我想像唔到，如果我free and easy 岀下夜街，行下街市冷巷會有幾大煲&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n利申：我唔知愛沙係北歐定東歐，只係分享下自已經歷"},{"pid":"c32a43c380c4d7a5e2f27212373735701d75f682","tid":359571,"uid":41375,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-15T05:55:26.000Z","msg":"未去過意大利 不過聽講南意同北意係兩個世界黎<br />\n<br />\n有冇人可以講多d<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}